--- xochitla2006 <xochitla2006@...> wrote:

> nightstrike/Darkfate:
> 
> both bots landed close to Deepstrike and Nightstrike said "We're 
> ready, what's the plan?"

Tumult and Decibel look at each other and then back at Nightstrike and
Darkfate. 

"The plan . . . " Decibel says in her loud booming voice is to learn
about you first! You see, we don't know much about you, and we need to
know how to fit you into our plan!"

A slightly pained looked passed over Tumult's face as Decibel spoke.
"While it's not very diplomatic, that's the truth." Tumult hooked a
thumb at Decebel, "She can be overly direct sometimes."

Decibel glared at Tumult, "I'm standing right here, you don't have to
talk about me as if I wasn't here!"

"You see?" Tumult responded as he ignored Decibel's outburst for the
moment, "This mission is military manuever, and we need to know what
your capable of before we take you out with us. We don't want any
rookie mistakes."

Decibel' face darkened as she continued to glare at Tumult! If it's one
thing she hated, it was being ignored!

Preston
